item.description:
In reply to &lt;a href=&quot;./../../blazor-how-to-ready-window-dimensions/index.html#comment-9&quot;&gt;Sumit Khaitan&lt;/a&gt;.

you need to call `StateHasChanged();` to refresh the UI.
&lt;code&gt;
    protected override async Task OnAfterRenderAsync(bool firstRender)
    {
        await GetDimensions();
        StateHasChanged();
    }
&lt;/code&gt;

